metadata.name: Homage to the Relic
metadata.description:
From the depths of time a relic appeared. A machine of metal from a distant year.

The ancients who built it have long since decayed. Its purpose unknown, its secrets delayed.

A million years it lay dormant and free…

atop it is written “2023”.

An altar is built around it. Both superstition and new technologies are used to try to ascertain its function. 

Midjourney V4 + ChatGPT V5 (edited)
